{"tid":715110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我信呢個世界有報應嘅","createTime":"2018-06-24T08:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T08:17:55.000Z","uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ccc83e013365f5cd5a6121474905aaf1d3b409","tid":715110,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"你點樣咁仆街咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家有幾折墮你之後咪一次過受晒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗諗吓其實我本身真係唔鍾意你，係咁啱你坐係我隔離姐。時間耐左先知道原來我都唔係好鍾意你不過你嗰日點樣hurt我同埋你之後做嘅嘢我真係好想快啲睇到你收皮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到有幾對唔住，乜嘢真係好想鍾意返我我聽到真係笑撚咗出嚟，10日都冇約個男仔出街食飯跟住一齊，你是最棒的。我想你快啲收皮冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我咁嬲你唔係因為仲好鍾意你，而係用一個旁觀者角度你真係一個大仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e95c5d98dd3e642e48afc903dca8a97ff88fca","tid":715110,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T08:17:55.000Z","msg":"波台狗嘅下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}